139
00:11:01,239 --> 00:11:03,000
Yue Yue, jangan salahkan pak cik
kerana cakap ini.

140
00:11:03,119 --> 00:11:04,960
Awak dah ada banyak jasa ketenteraan.

141
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,479
Sudah tiba masanya awak cari

142
