146
00:11:14,161 --> 00:11:15,239
Biarpun awak rasa pak cik kuat berleter

147
00:11:15,239 --> 00:11:16,239
dan nak halau pak cik setiap kali,

148
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,960
pak cik perlu nasihati awak.

149
