Pak cik akan meleteri awak
setiap kali jumpa awak.

150
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:21,799
Baik, jom.

151
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:23,320
Jom pergi main di situ.

152
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,640
Lihatlah.

153
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,000
Betul cakap Pak Cik Zhao.

154
00:11:34,599 --> 00:11:36,679
Setiap orang harus ada keluarga sendiri.

155
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:41,000
Selepas menghapuskan musuh di luar,

156
00:11:41,359 --> 00:11:42,479
