166
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,599
(saya boleh rasai)

167
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,359
(awak Raja Naga saya.)

168
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,320
Lapor!

169
00:12:53,479 --> 00:12:55,080
