170
00:12:55,239 --> 00:12:56,080
Silakan dia masuk.

171
00:12:58,520 --> 00:12:59,919
Tuan Lu.

172
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,080
Saya minta baginda

173
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,039
untuk membenarkan saya datang ke sini
sebagai Pemantau Angkatan Tentera lagi.

174
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,359
Tempat ini sunyi sepi,

175
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,919
tak boleh berbanding dengan Fengdu.

176
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,479
Saya sanggup datang
tak kira betapa susah.

177
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:34,640
Jangan-jangan awak
tak faham isi hati saya?

178
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,440
Abang Zheng,

179
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,640
