180
00:13:48,679 --> 00:13:49,679
Buah hati?

181
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:51,919
Chenyue, saya faham.

182
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:55,320
Chenyue, jika awak nak menolak saya,

183
