194
00:14:28,679 --> 00:14:30,119
dan ia tak pernah hilang,

195
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,000
malah jadi semakin kuat.

196
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,479
Maafkan saya.

197
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:43,080
Awak tak perlu minta maaf daripada saya.

198
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,520
Kenapa awak beritahu saya semua ini?

199
00:14:46,919 --> 00:14:47,880
Abang Zheng,

200
00:14:48,239 --> 00:14:49,080
awak pasti akan temui

201
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,400
kebahagiaan awak.

202
00:14:55,599 --> 00:14:56,799
Jadi, kelak,

203
