Abang Zheng, betul?

204
00:15:02,719 --> 00:15:03,799
Tentulah.

205
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,000
Raja Naga!

206
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:01,919
Saya tahu awak berada di sisi saya!

207
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,599
Kenapa awak enggan berdepan dengan saya?

208
00:16:12,359 --> 00:16:13,320
Raja Naga,

209
00:16:15,559 --> 00:16:16,919
awak akan datang cari saya,

210
00:16:18,599 --> 00:16:19,640
