211
00:16:22,799 --> 00:16:23,719
(Chenyue,)

212
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:26,000
(maafkan saya sebab tak boleh
berdepan dengan awak)

213
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,679
(dan beritahu awak kebenaran.)

214
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:31,039
(Namun, saya akan berada
di sisi awak buat selama-lamanya.)

215
00:16:57,562 --> 00:16:58,799
Banyaknya kupu-kupu.

216
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,520
Abang Yuchi, cepat tengok.

217
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,680
Kupu-kupu ini tahu sifat manusia.

218
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,199
Abang Yuchi.

219
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:32,640
(Raja Naga,)

220
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,400
(saya dah tahu jawapannya.)

221
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,920
Separuh hari saja berlalu.

222
00:18:49,239 --> 00:18:50,640
Luka awak sembuh dengan cepat sekali.

223
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,199
Luka saya tak parah.

224
00:18:57,119 --> 00:18:58,520
Berapa lama awak nak melindungi saya?

225
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,199
Selama-lamanya.

226
00:19:04,599 --> 00:19:05,800
Jangan mungkir janji.

227
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:08,079
