dengan hati yang tak tenang♪

230
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,280
(Saya tahu,)

231
00:19:21,479 --> 00:19:22,800
(awak tak boleh beritahu saya
identiti sebenar awak)

232
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:25,119
(atas sebab tertentu.)

233
00:19:26,239 --> 00:19:27,239
(Tak apa.)

234
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,079
(Asalkan awak berada di sisi saya
buat selama-lamanya,)

235
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:33,199
(saya tak kisah apa-apa lagi,)

236
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,640
